  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains what data is collected, how it is used, and how it is protected when using our app.</p>

  <h2>1. Data Collected</h2>
  <p>When you use the app, any message you send is transmitted to our server. The following data may be collected and stored:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>User messages entered in the app</li>
    <li>Technical information required for transmission (e.g. time of request, connection logs)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Purpose of Processing</h2>
  <p>The collected messages are processed to provide the appâ€™s functionality. Specifically:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your message is sent from our server to the ChatGPT API in order to generate a response.</li>
    <liYour message is stored in our server database to improve service functionality, allow conversation history, and provide support if needed.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>Your message content is shared with the ChatGPT service (OpenAI) for processing. OpenAI processes the message to generate a reply, which is then returned to you via our app.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>User messages are stored in our server database. They will be kept only as long as necessary to provide the service and support, unless a longer retention is required by law.</p>

  <h2>5. User Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to request access, correction, or deletion of your data. You can contact us anytime to exercise these rights.</p>

  <h2>6. Contact</h2>
  <p>Windtalkerz<br>
  E-mail: <a href="mailto:support@blackpearls.com">support@blackpearls.com</a></p>

  <p>Last updated: September 2025</p>
